data.title: LAB 3 Laptops and All in One
data.meta_description: LAB 3 Laptops and All in One - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides instructions for a lab on laptop and all-in-one computer hardware. The objectives are to remove components from a Dell laptop and all-in-one Mac system, including the battery, memory, hard drive, optical drive, keyboard, and other parts. Students are instructed to work in pairs, use proper materials and precautions, and have an instructor verify their work at several check points. The purpose is to gain hands-on experience accessing and removing internal parts of laptop and all-in-one computers.
